• Obtaining of new professional competences of Computer Technique and Technologies specialty: skills for assembling computer technique; constructing, configuring and and administering of computer networks; webs programming and design; meeting the newest models of computer technique on the market;
• contribution to the foreign language teaching, behavioral and inrer- cultural skills through meeting the host’s culture and traditions: working in a particular occupation environment in a country of the European Union; enriching the culture of the demeanor; meeting the the history and traditions of Spain;
• making long- lasting contacts between partners with goal- exchange of ideas, programmes and future mobilities;
• increasing the authority of our secondary school by qualified professional preparation;
• our choice was done after careful researching of the experience of organizations, that could be appropriate for the implementation of our project. Having in mind the number of the successful projects, we chose the Training Vision Ltd partner. It has got a rich experience of organization and implementation of professional practice in European educational programmes Leonardo de Vinci, Erasmus and Grundvig. Also, the Training Vision Ltd gives us an opportunity to gather economical, historical and social impressions for the town- host and the country.
